{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Make coercive or controlling behaviour leading to suicide a specific offence",
        "additional_details": "We call for urgent reform to make coercion leading to suicide within domestic abuse cases a specific offence, ensuring perpetrators face justice in Crown Court. This is not just a legal need, but a moral one.",
        "background": "Domestic violence and coercive control can destroy lives, sometimes driving victims to suicide. Yet the law fails to recognise this as a specific criminal offence. ",
